@node "intro" "Introduction..."

  APSearch 1.2 is a program to researching files and directories to find
 entering string.

  This program is FREEWARE and it's freely distributable as long as all of
 its files are included in their original form.No fee is charged for its
 distribution.

  All suggestions and comments about this program please send on the follo-
  wing address :
